REFERRED TO COMMERCE, ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AND SMALL BUSINESS

Title: Provides for a waiver of certain liquor license renewal fees
Summary: Provides for a waiver of certain liquor license renewal fees; provides for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to waiving certain liquor license renewal fees; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
